title: Live updates: Trump’s Gaza plan doesn’t include troops, U.S. funds to rebuild, White House says amid backlash
description: President Donald Trump proposed the United States take a “long-term ownership position” over Gaza and permanently displace its residents. Hamas condemned the plan.
author: Abbie Cheeseman, Niha Masih, Frances Vinall, Victoria Bisset, Victoria Craw, Sammy Westfall, Michael Birnbaum
